        "code": "/**\n * {@inheritDoc}\n */\n@Override\nprotected void writeChildren(FreeColXMLWriter xw) throws XMLStreamException {\n    super.writeChildren(xw);\n    for (ProductionType productionType : productionTypes) {\n        productionType.toXML(xw);\n    }\n}"
